Distribution . To date only known from the type locality, the sandy gravelly margins of the Matjies River, on the edge of the Cederberg range in the Western Cape Province, South Africa . This locality is situated in a region which is somewhat transitional between the fynbos and succulent karoo biomes (Murcinia &
Rutherford, 2006
); fynbos occurring at higher altitudes, lower altitude sites such as the type locality being surrounded by succulent karoo.
